'''Sumerian唱片'''（{{lang|en|Sumerian Records}}）是一間美國[[獨立音樂|獨立音樂]]唱片公司，位於[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]和[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]。該唱片公司於2006年成立<ref>"Label Profile: Sumerian Records". ''Alternative Press'' #263 (June 2010), p. 38.</ref>，創辦人為書商''Ash Avildsen''，並由''Shawn Keith''管理<ref name="Veil">"[http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=88269 VEIL OF MAYA Signs With SUMERIAN RECORDS] {{Wayback|url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=88269 |date=20110606081837 }}", Blabbermouth.net, January 11, 2008, retrieved 2010-03-27</ref><ref name="Fell">"[http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=105951 FELLSILENT Inks U.S. Deal With SUMERIAN RECORDS] {{Wayback|url=http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=105951 |date=20110606081954 }}", Blabbermouth.net, October 1, 2008, retrieved 2010-03-27</ref> 

==公司歷史==
2008年，樂團''Fellsilent''成為該公司所簽的第一隊非美國樂隊<ref name="Fell" /> 該唱片公司與''Rock Band''遊戲系列合作，將其音樂帶到''Rock Band Network''。至今，旗下樂團[[Asking_Alexandria|Asking Alexandria]]的音樂，包括''The Final Episode (Let's Change the Channel)''、''A Prophecy''、''Hey There Mr. Brook''已在該遊戲中出現。而樂團[[Veil_of_Maya|Veil of Maya]]和[[After_the_Burial|After the Burial]]的音樂亦將會在遊戲中推出。<ref>{{cite web|title=Sumerian Records to Debut on Rock Band Network with Asking Alexandria!|url=http://www.rhythmauthors.com/news/2010/04/30/sumerian-records-debut-rbn-asking-alexandria|publisher=Rhythm Authors|accessdate=1 December 2010|date=30 April 2010|archive-date=2011-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008202326/http://www.rhythmauthors.com/news/2010/04/30/sumerian-records-debut-rbn-asking-alexandria|dead-url=no}}</ref>
2011年二月，Sumerian重新與[[死亡金屬|死亡金屬]]樂團[[The_Faceless|The Faceless]]簽約，Avildsen認為這是唱片公司有史以來最具象徵性與紀念性的簽約。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theprp.com/2011/02/08/news/the-faceless-re-sign-with-sumerian-new-album-in-the-works/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-10-23 |archive-date=2011-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110921092753/http://www.theprp.com/2011/02/08/news/the-faceless-re-sign-with-sumerian-new-album-in-the-works/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
五月，他們簽下了澳洲樂團[[Dead_Letter_Circus|Dead Letter Circus]]。創辦人表示：「真榮幸可以和如此這一群優秀的作曲家和富有遠見的音樂人簽約。搖滾在我們公司會有新的世代，而[[Dead_Letter_Circus|Dead Letter Circus]]就是未來。」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.smnnews.com/2011/05/19/dead-letter-circus-announces-its-signing-with-sumerian-records/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308041509/http://www.smnnews.com/2011/05/19/dead-letter-circus-announces-its-signing-with-sumerian-records/ |archive-date=2016-03-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

